27;s all right.</span><br><span class=\"line\">我喃喃自语 真的没有关系</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sun, sun, sun, here it comes...</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳啊 太阳啊 太阳啊 你总算出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sun, sun, sun, here it comes...</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳啊 太阳啊 太阳啊 你总算出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sun, sun, sun, here it comes...</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳啊 太阳啊 太阳啊 你总算出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sun, sun, sun, here it comes...</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳啊 太阳啊 太阳啊 你总算出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sun, sun, sun, here it comes...</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳啊 太阳啊 太阳啊 你总算出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">Little darling, I feel that ice is slowly melting.</span><br><span class=\"line\">小宝贝 我感到寒冰正在点滴融化</span><br><span class=\"line\">Little darling, it seems like years since it&#x27;s been clear.</span><br><span class=\"line\">小宝贝 自从冬天降临似乎又过了多年</span><br><span class=\"line\">Here comes the sun, here comes the sun,</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳算是出来啦 太阳出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">and I say, it&#x27;s all right.</span><br><span class=\"line\">我喃喃自语 真的没有关系</span><br><span class=\"line\">Here comes the sun, here comes the sun.</span><br><span class=\"line\">太阳终于出来啦 太阳出来啦</span><br><span class=\"line\">It&#x27;s all right.</span><br><span class=\"line\">真的没有关系</span><br><span class=\"line\">It&#x27;s all right.</span><br><span class=\"line\">真的没有关系</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n","more":"</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br